I think there might be some confusion! As a conversational AI, I don't have personal preferences or dietary restrictions, but I can certainly help you with yours!

If you have any specific food preferences or dietary restrictions, such as vegetarian, vegan, gluten-free, or others, please let me know. I can provide you with personalized recommendations for Osaka's food scene that cater to your needs.

Additionally, if you have any other questions or topics you'd like to discuss, feel free to ask!
